task.summary:
Moved IOService to the shield.
IOService is common to all the boost related asio services which means other parts which are using boost::asio should be able to use it.

Bug Fixes and much more.
- Default black color for CameraView - TelematicsEvent should be fired only to those who have same bot id as of event - Added TelematicsView for UI - App now inherits View - Layout should update child only when child is dirty. - Added option of font style - onCreate should be called only once
Wait-lock mechanism not required as of now.
